Company Overview of Arrowgrass Capital Partners LLP



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Arrowgrass Capital Partners LLP is a privately owned hedge fund sponsor. The firm invests in the alternative markets across the globe. It employs value and event driven strategies to make its investments. Arrowgrass Capital Partners was founded in 2007 and is based in London, United Kingdom with additional office in New York, New York.


3rd Floor10 Portman SquareMaryleboneLondon,  W1H 6AZUnited KingdomFounded in 2007



Phone: 44 20 3100 1000

Fax: 44 20 3100 1310

www.arrowgrass.com







