Arrowgrass Capital Partners LLP


                  Arrowgrass is an active, cycle-agnostic, European focused manager which follows a global multi-strategy investment approach including relative value and event-driven sub strategies. They typically invest across a range of sectors.  The firm draws on strategies such as volatility arbitrage, convertible arbitrage, special situations, distressed and capital structure arbitrage and merger arbitrage.                




Portfolio Manager

                                    2008 - 2015                


Man GLG


                  GLG is an active manager which combines fundamental analysis with tactical trading, emphasizing utilizing qualitative and quantitative analysis to invest globally in private equity and fixed-income. For their alternative investments, they aim to deliver attractive risk-adjusted returns driven by security selection. For their long-only strategies, they aim to deliver above-index performance through an active investment philosophy focusing on alpha capture.The firm uses a global macro investment approach that includes long/short, convertible arbitrage, special situations and distressed debt strategies. Alternative investments are made through options, futures and convertibles. They construct concentrated portfolios and favor market leaders that have a competitive advantage.                





